
```py
>>> x = np.linspace(johnsonsu.ppf(0.01, a, b),
...                 johnsonsu.ppf(0.99, a, b), 100)

...        'r-', lw=5, alpha=0.6, label='johnsonsu pdf') 
```

```py
>>> rv = johnsonsu(a, b)
>>> ax.plot(x, rv.pdf(x), 'k-', lw=2, label='frozen pdf') 
```

